{"type": "article", "id": 8681, "title": "Urushi 自行车", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-20T07:28:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235328EKWakwPL74dyhOTo.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tPaul Smith Milano 店是米兰国际交通展会的承办展区，这里将在米兰家具展上展出全球仅限量 9 辆的 Vanhulsteijn 自行车。这款名为 “Urushi” 的自行车采取的是日本传统的设计风格，其表面采用的是 Urushi 生漆技术，这种技术工艺极为复杂，需要提取漆树的汁液，配合贵金属箔，最终形成光彩夺目的视觉效果。这款车的价格现在未定，需要根据现场需求确定。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052353246vMmrfTQJYeysPzg.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.68796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235325Hpn3mlDKi8urGRxk.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.94814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052353259ouSPWbL3TXmQCZR.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523532630OrlaC7bH6RqdEI.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235326YFiIHKA81bZuyWoP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.67625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235327WtdjXLTvBOmZAcIG.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235327GskIPTYEfOBqcuDF.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}